I '''Rodrigo Garcia y Robertson''' (mibait anyang 1949) metung yang [[Estados Unidos|American]]ung talasulat ning pangkasalesayan a ampong pantasyang pikudta (historical and fantasy fiction).  Atin yang  [[Ph.D]] king amlat (history) at tinuru ya king [[UCLA]] ampo king [[Villanova University]] bayu ing pamaniulat ing megi nang manimunang propesion. Bukud kareng walu nang nobela, dakal ya makuyad a salita (short story) a milimbag kareng pamitipun o anthology king pantasya ampong pikudtang syensya (science fiction). Manuknangan ya king [[Mount Vernon, Washington]].

